Typedef Documentation

typedef struct _dcid_info_t dcid_info_t

DCID information.

This structure should be passed to dcid_create() in order to initialize a DCID instance.

typedef struct _dcid_t dcid_t

DCID instance.

This structure represents an instance of the DCID.
